{"tid":1593331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建立香港人集體意志嘅清算平台","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:12:48.000Z","uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f890bcb1065a543c505edd29dcaaee0577ac4650","tid":1593331,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"Refer返我之前嘅Post<br />\n<br />\n大家9月8日去美國領館好似爭樣嘢.......<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545497</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我IT 力不足，只係諗到用FB Page，建立足夠嘅Like數，再用Google Form比大家輸入制裁名單，包括個人資料，所屬機構/團體，職位，罪行Source。<br />\n<br />\n然後每日Gen 個Google Sheet出嚟比大家睇返，等大家唔洗重覆輸入，然後連署同埋去信美國國務卿，由香港人自己提供，唔比人騎劫。<br />\n<br />\n希望集思廣益，集合大家嘅IT力同想法，可以合力將制裁名單制作出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n有幾個問題要面對：<br />\n1. 重覆輸入<br />\n2. 做唔到Live Update，有可能會比搞個Database<br />\n3. 點先確保Hold住個Database嘅人嘅可信性"},{"pid":"020a5611c76fa729c206d79972bbf66cc0b953ad","tid":1593331,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"9d5b414d8075b1775f7bb866597c879c232b28f6","tid":1593331,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a30ad674a366359d19fea8108ed76559a6f5f4c","tid":1593331,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:07:35.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"6fce0a91e1ada3c95d190b5f294f3be3e73ff72e","tid":1593331,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e23e07541c52212cb31508743b5d03fc74e0377","tid":1593331,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"